Current placement matches should be for the [preseason ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/231832207-Preseason-FAQ)of your selected queue.  Season 7 has not started yet, so no games will be counted towards the season until it actually begins.  Hope that helps bring some ease.
